winner tonight is Dividr

00:09:01.326 --> 00:09:04.976
by Josh Deichmann, Patrick
Pistor, and Erik Lydick.

00:09:05.516 --> 00:09:13.686
[ Applause ]

00:09:14.186 --> 00:09:14.646
Congratulations.

