00:40:41.286 --> 00:40:42.836
so let me show you
guys how it's done.

00:40:47.516 --> 00:40:50.006
[ Laughter ]

00:40:50.506 --> 00:40:52.566
There must be a problem
with this iPad.

00:40:53.046 --> 00:40:55.046
[ Laughter ]

00:40:55.076 --> 00:40:55.976
All right, let me redeem myself.

00:40:56.516 --> 00:41:00.026
[ Laughter ]

00:41:00.526 --> 00:41:05.436
Oh, man. OK, this was a
lot easier in rehearsals

00:41:05.436 --> 00:41:07.506
