Bam! That's how I do!

00:41:31.516 --> 00:41:33.546
[ Laughter ]

00:41:34.046 --> 00:41:34.886
All right.

00:41:35.386 --> 00:41:37.976
So what I want to show you
guys is some of the levels

00:41:37.976 --> 00:41:40.646
that really demonstrate
the highly realistic INKS

00:41:40.646 --> 00:41:41.896
that I was talking
about earlier.

00:41:42.586 --> 00:41:44.976
So there's that big color
swatch in the center.

00:41:45.096 --> 00:41:49.126
