colors continue to blend

00:41:53.986 --> 00:41:56.176
into each other and
darken as they go.

00:41:56.176 --> 00:41:59.506
The team spent a lot of
time studying water colors,

00:41:59.506 --> 00:42:01.976
the physics of it, the
dynamics, how it dries

00:42:02.036 --> 00:42:03.996
into the paper and blends.

00:42:03.996 --> 00:42:05.236
It's really gorgeous.

00:42:05.236 --> 00:42:07.746
And I'll show you just
one more level here

00:42:08.816 --> 00:42:10.796
