00:42:33.836 --> 00:42:36.216
attention to detail and
care, create something

00:42:36.216 --> 00:42:37.936
which is completely
fresh and unique.

00:42:38.356 --> 00:42:38.976
Brilliant job.

00:42:38.976 --> 00:42:39.816
Thanks. Back to you.

