I can look more closely

00:47:05.626 --> 00:47:06.996
at the details on the screen --

00:47:07.266 --> 00:47:10.566
perhaps the exact
posture of the instructor.

00:47:11.116 --> 00:47:14.326
Now this is possible and is
beyond the standard controls

00:47:14.326 --> 00:47:18.046
because Zova has implemented
a custom AVPlayerLayer.

00:47:20.046 --> 00:47:22.396
Similarly, if I was
to swipe left,

00:47:22.626 --> 00:47:25.616
I can restart an
exercise very quickly.

00:47:26.196 --> 00:47:32.376
