00:47:50.956 --> 00:47:55.746
And through HealthKit and
my iPhone, it is overlaying

00:47:55.746 --> 00:47:57.846
that onto the live
video stream here.

00:47:57.846 --> 00:47:59.376
So that's my heartrate
you're looking at.

00:48:03.326 --> 00:48:04.246
Let's move along then.

00:48:07.506 --> 00:48:11.586
At the end of each workout, you
have an opportunity to, I guess,

00:48:11.586 --> 00:48:13.816
log your feedback as
to how you've done.

00:48:14.196 --> 00:48:16.346
