thumbs-up for it has gone well,

00:48:20.196 --> 00:48:21.776
or if it's gone less well --

00:48:21.776 --> 00:48:27.406
and in my case, I tend to
quiver my lips a little, too.

00:48:27.406 --> 00:48:27.976
So there you go.

