like to turn it over to Michael.

00:50:17.556 --> 00:50:18.076
>> Thank you, John.

00:50:18.676 --> 00:50:20.586
So Ulysses is a focused

00:50:20.586 --> 00:50:22.806
and distraction-free
writing environment.

00:50:23.396 --> 00:50:26.416
It has the power of
classic word processers

00:50:26.416 --> 00:50:29.176
with flexible organization
and management tools.

00:50:29.176 --> 00:50:32.926
Now it's a super clean writing
experience and it has features

00:50:32.926 --> 00:50:34.316
to help you through the task.

00:50:34.756 --> 00:50:36.066
So the first thing, for example,

00:50:36.476 --> 00:50:38.836
is I can highlight
the current line.

00:50:38.836 --> 00:50:40.596
That should look familiar.

00:50:41.266 --> 00:50:44.136
We can also show
paragraph numbers.

00:50:45.266 --> 00:50:47.616
Now Ulysses is based
on Markdown.

00:50:48.066 --> 00:50:49.236
