through about 1.3 million words,

00:52:35.356 --> 00:52:36.946
most of those written
by James Joyce.

00:52:37.326 --> 00:52:39.916
And that's thanks to their
implementation of Spotlight

00:52:39.916 --> 00:52:41.376
