01:02:21.096 --> 01:02:24.546
And it does tie into
building something that's fun,

01:02:24.546 --> 01:02:27.426
and unique, and compelling.

01:02:27.946 --> 01:02:33.106
So to talk about that, I'd like
to invite Ben Wolstenholme,

01:02:33.106 --> 01:02:39.386
Cofounder and CEO of Madefire, a
developer of iOS and TV OS apps,

01:02:39.476 --> 01:02:40.636
to join me here on stage.

01:02:40.636 --> 01:02:40.816
Ben?

01:02:41.516 --> 01:02:50.576
[ Applause ]

01:02:51.076 --> 01:02:51.586
Thanks, John.

01:02:51.696 --> 01:02:52.366
Great to be here.

01:02:52.776 --> 01:02:57.106
So Madefire is all
about storytelling --

01:02:57.576 --> 01:03:00.156
and in particular, comics.

01:03:01.036 --> 01:03:02.906
We love comics because they're

01:03:02.906 --> 01:03:05.276
such a powerful storytelling
format.

01:03:06.226 --> 01:03:07.746
People learn to read
through comics.

01:03:08.396 --> 01:03:10.636
People escape into other
worlds through comics.

01:03:11.576 --> 01:03:15.766
Most of all, comics are
words and pictures perfect

01:03:15.896 --> 01:03:19.276
for the visual world
that we live in.

01:03:19.666 --> 01:03:22.196
We've been working closely with
Apple on something that we'd

01:03:22.196 --> 01:03:23.476
like to share with you tonight.

01:03:24.926 --> 01:03:26.076
As you may have seen earlier,

01:03:26.316 --> 01:03:29.476
Apple today launched new
app review guidelines.

01:03:30.486 --> 01:03:31.966
They're very different
to the guidelines

01:03:31.966 --> 01:03:34.636
that we're all used to, and
they're much more approachable.

01:03:35.936 --> 01:03:38.806
And after speaking with Apple
about this new approach,

01:03:39.806 --> 01:03:45.476
we collaborated to create --

01:03:46.516 --> 01:03:52.546
[ Applause ]

01:03:53.046 --> 01:03:57.606
Oh, yes! App Review
Guidelines, the Comic Book.

01:03:58.056 --> 01:04:02.396
OK. Apple has put a lot of
thought into reorganizing

01:04:02.396 --> 01:04:04.886
and simplifying the
guidelines into five sections.

01:04:05.676 --> 01:04:08.066
And this gave us a great
opportunity to work

01:04:08.066 --> 01:04:09.316
with different illustrators

01:04:09.686 --> 01:04:14.376
and to develop five totally
different graphic styles.

01:04:14.556 --> 01:04:17.006
Each section is a visual story.

01:04:18.016 --> 01:04:20.076
And we really wanted
the visuals to react

01:04:20.366 --> 01:04:22.696
with the serious content
of the guidelines.

01:04:23.536 --> 01:04:26.226
It's created a pretty
wild outcome,

01:04:27.666 --> 01:04:29.596
and something we hope
will engage people

01:04:30.086 --> 01:04:33.266
around these important
topics even

01:04:33.266 --> 01:04:35.446
if you think you know
the guidelines already.

01:04:36.196 --> 01:04:37.646
It's pretty useful.

01:04:38.596 --> 01:04:41.466
The comic book will be
available for download

01:04:41.466 --> 01:04:42.786
from the developer's site,

01:04:42.786 --> 01:04:45.086
alongside the searchable
text version.

01:04:45.936 --> 01:04:50.736
But you will get to take home
your printed comic book tonight.

01:04:51.516 --> 01:04:58.806
[ Applause ]

01:04:59.306 --> 01:05:02.226
Oh, yes, hard to believe.

01:05:02.426 --> 01:05:04.956
In a world of screens,
a big part of what we do

01:05:04.956 --> 01:05:07.056
at Madefire is enable people

01:05:07.316 --> 01:05:09.996
to turn their stories
into motion books.

01:05:10.966 --> 01:05:14.086
As you can see, motion books
are a reading experience

01:05:14.366 --> 01:05:16.186
with motion, sound, and depth.

01:05:17.316 --> 01:05:21.286
And we're thrilled to be
working on a motion book version

01:05:21.666 --> 01:05:23.276
of the app review guidelines.

01:05:24.746 --> 01:05:27.956
Here's a sneak peek.

01:05:28.516 --> 01:05:58.546
[ Music ]

01:05:59.046 --> 01:06:02.786
So, look out for the App Review
Guidelines motion book coming

01:06:02.786 --> 01:06:05.106
soon to an Apple
device near you.

01:06:05.996 --> 01:06:08.576
And you can get your
printed comic here tonight.

01:06:08.626 --> 01:06:10.286
I hope you enjoy the read.

01:06:10.686 --> 01:06:10.886
Thanks.

01:06:11.516 --> 01:06:18.556
[ Applause ]

01:06:19.056 --> 01:06:19.686
Thanks, ben.

